CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1962, pg. 9 reads: "Mr. and Mrs. Charles Walker...married at St. James - Frances Clark, daughter of Mrs. Ethel Clark of Brushton, was married in St. James Roman Catholic Church July 21st, to Charles Walker, son of Mrs. Emma Walker, of San Mateo, Calif..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: unknown woman, possibly Emma Walker, Groom Charles Walker, Bride Frances Clark Walker wearing knee length short sleeved jacquard dress and wrist corsage, and unknown woman, possibly Ethel Clark, posed in living room, horizontal format
